# profile/.denylist — strings the pre-commit hook refuses to let into commits.
#
# Copy to ../profile/.denylist (the onboarding skill does this automatically).
# One literal per line. Lines starting with `#` and blank lines are ignored.
# Matching is case-insensitive substring.
#
# The framework baseline already covers generic credential patterns and
# the original-maintainer identifiers — see scripts/safety/denylist_check.py.
# Add the strings below that should also never leak from your machine.

# Company / brand
# YourCompany Inc.
# AcmeProductName

# Customers / accounts
# (one per line)

# Executives / employees (full names)
# (one per line)

# Internal codenames
# project-aurora
